32#ifndef _LINUX_RESERVATION_H_
33#define _LINUX_RESERVATION_H_
34
35#include <linux/fence.h>
36#include <linux/rcupdate.h>
37#include <linux/ww_mutex.h>
38
39struct reservation_object {
40 struct ww_mutex lock;
41
42 unsigned robj_version;
43 struct fence __rcu *robj_fence;
44 struct reservation_object_list __rcu *robj_list;
45 struct reservation_object_list __rcu *robj_prealloc;
46};
47
48struct reservation_object_list {
49 struct rcu_head rol_rcu;
50
51 uint32_t shared_count;
52 uint32_t shared_max;
53 struct fence __rcu *shared[];
54};
55
56/* NetBSD addition */
57struct reservation_poll {
58 kmutex_t rp_lock;
59 struct selinfo rp_selq;
60 struct fence_cb rp_fcb;
61 bool rp_claimed;
62};
63
64#define reservation_object_add_excl_fence linux_reservation_object_add_excl_fence
65#define reservation_object_add_shared_fence linux_reservation_object_add_shared_fence
66#define reservation_object_fini linux_reservation_object_fini
67#define reservation_object_get_excl linux_reservation_object_get_excl
68#define reservation_object_get_fences_rcu linux_reservation_object_get_fences_rcu
69#define reservation_object_get_list linux_reservation_object_get_list
70#define reservation_object_held linux_reservation_object_held
71#define reservation_object_init linux_reservation_object_init
72#define reservation_object_kqfilter linux_reservation_object_kqfilter
73#define reservation_object_poll linux_reservation_object_poll
74#define reservation_object_reserve_shared linux_reservation_object_reserve_shared
75#define reservation_object_test_signaled_rcu linux_reservation_object_test_signaled_rcu
76#define reservation_object_wait_timeout_rcu linux_reservation_object_wait_timeout_rcu
77#define reservation_poll_fini linux_reservation_poll_fini
78#define reservation_poll_init linux_reservation_poll_init
79#define reservation_ww_class linux_reservation_ww_class
80
81extern struct ww_class reservation_ww_class;
82
83void reservation_object_init(struct reservation_object *);
84void reservation_object_fini(struct reservation_object *);
85bool reservation_object_held(struct reservation_object *);
86struct fence *
87 reservation_object_get_excl(struct reservation_object *);
88struct reservation_object_list *
89 reservation_object_get_list(struct reservation_object *);
90int reservation_object_reserve_shared(struct reservation_object *);
91void reservation_object_add_excl_fence(struct reservation_object *,
92 struct fence *);
93void reservation_object_add_shared_fence(struct reservation_object *,
94 struct fence *);
95
96int reservation_object_get_fences_rcu(struct reservation_object *,
97 struct fence **, unsigned *, struct fence ***);
98
99bool reservation_object_test_signaled_rcu(struct reservation_object *,
100 bool);
101long reservation_object_wait_timeout_rcu(struct reservation_object *,
102 bool, bool, unsigned long);
103
104/* NetBSD additions */
105void reservation_poll_init(struct reservation_poll *);
106void reservation_poll_fini(struct reservation_poll *);
107int reservation_object_poll(struct reservation_object *, int,
108 struct reservation_poll *);
109int reservation_object_kqfilter(struct reservation_object *,
110 struct knote *, struct reservation_poll *);
111
112#endif /* _LINUX_RESERVATION_H_ */
